"tecnología avanza. Ya sea para tu desarrollo personal o profesional, este "
"curso sienta las bases para tu camino en TI."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:elearning_platform.product_template_67
msgid ""
"With <strong>lifetime access</strong>, you’ll have the freedom to learn at "
"your own pace and revisit techniques whenever you need a refresher. Whether "
